msgid "action_setformation_short_name"
msgstr "Set Formation"

msgid "set_formation_action_name"
msgstr "Set Formation"

msgid "set_formation_description"
msgstr "Set a formation in the current region. Requires an equipped formation disk and consumes spirit stones. Each region can have only one active formation at a time; a new formation replaces the existing one. The Spirit-Gathering Formation increases breathing cultivation gains and suits cultivation regions and sect headquarters. The Mountain-Guard Formation improves combat capability within the formation and suits sect headquarters and cultivation regions. The Healing Formation improves healing recovery and suits sect headquarters, cultivation regions, and cities. The Clarity Formation improves seclusion and breakthrough stability and suits cultivation regions and sect headquarters. The Vein-Seeking Formation increases mining gains and suits normal regions with mineral lodes. The Wood-Growth Formation increases gathering gains and suits normal regions with plants. The Beast-Driving Formation increases hunting gains and suits normal regions with animals."

msgid "set_formation_requirements"
msgstr "Requires an equipped formation disk, a valid location for the selected formation, and enough spirit stones."

